<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٠٧٤ - حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ نُمَيْرٍ، عَنْ حَنْظَلَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْقَاسِمِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنْ شَاءَتْ فَلْتَجْمَعْ بَيْنَهُمَا»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>